comments: Fultz (ORL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Thomas (WAS) and does not affect his SQBR.
Beal (WAS) makes incidental contact with Gordon (ORL) that does not affect his FOM.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes a legal screening position in Beal's (WAS) path and does not deliver contact.
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Fournier's (ORL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Aminu (ORL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Beal's (WAS) path and does not deliver contact.
Beal (WAS) makes marginal contact with Fournier (ORL) but does not affect his ability to secure the pass.
Bertrans (WAS) initiates contact with Fournier (ORL) that affects his SQBR. The contact causes him to travel and a personal foul on Bertans should have been called instead.
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Fournier's (ORL) path and does not deliver contact.
Bryant (WAS) dislodges Vucevic (ORL) from his desired position in the post.
Fournier (ORL) makes incidental contact with Bryant (WAS) during the screen as he maintains his legal guarding position.
Beal (WAS) splits his feet to start his drive.
Thomas (WAS) makes incidental contact with Fultz (ORL) as both players attempt to get loose ball.
Bertans (WAS) makes contact Fultz's (ORL) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Beal (WAS) makes contact to the arm of Fournier (ORL) during the pass.
Miles (WAS) and Gordon (ORL) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Thomas (WAS) commits a take foul on Gordon (ORL).
Vucevic (ORL) maintains his legal guarding position as he defends Beal (WAS) and does not affect his SQBR.
